{"tid":255233,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"JTC Workshop 係雞係公廁, 小心中伏","createTime":"2017-05-23T18:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T10:04:20.000Z","uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f61b386a00016de625373d1954cab6e619b533","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/61011/-速遞員悲歌-連踩36小時麥當勞-百佳兼送-無聲無息被炒兼拖糧\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F61011%2F-%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E%E5%93%A1%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C-%E9%80%A3%E8%B8%A936%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E-%E7%99%BE%E4%BD%B3%E5%85%BC%E9%80%81-%E7%84%A1%E8%81%B2%E7%84%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92%E5%85%BC%E6%8B%96%E7%B3%A7&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=88692555\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/61011/-速遞員悲歌-連踩36小時麥當勞-百佳兼送-無聲無息被炒兼拖糧</a> <br />\n摘自HK01: <br />\n<blockquote>百佳、麥當勞將送貨服務外判予域迅快遞有限公司，而域迅則再外判予JTC Workshop。據悉，現時至少5名JTC Workshop員工被拖欠薪金，拖欠金額介乎1,000元至36,000元。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家向無良老闆查詢 <br />\n名:朱建威 <br />\nID: Z4398700 <br />\nTel: 63903255 <br />\n<br />\n無良業務資料: <br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/HbQZOnG.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHbQZOnG.jpg&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2fdf125c\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/HbQZOnG.jpg</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/2mL3EYZ.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2mL3EYZ.jpg&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d2297739\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/2mL3EYZ.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"ed3aea3e44cc811ff6a018aad71388285789e151","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"百佳、麥當勞將送貨服務外判予域迅快遞有限公司，而域迅則再外判予JTC Workshop。<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，現時至少5名JTC Workshop員工被拖欠薪金，拖欠金額介乎1,000元至36,000元。</span> <br />\n<br />\n曾被要求連續工作36小時　連做14天 <br />\n<br />\n30多歲的阿志(化名)過往任職司機，今年7月18日入職JTC Workshop，為麥當勞送外賣，惟10月13日工作期間「炒車」後，僱主只要求他翌日代班一天後，就再沒安排任何工作，亦沒表明將其解僱。他表示被拖欠10月1日至14日薪金，連同隧道費、加班費等，合共超過2萬元。<span style=\"color: red;\">入職3個月，阿志指僱主從未準時出糧</span>，之前公司於8月中才發放7月薪酬，而9月尾才發放8月薪酬，而公司更推搪指遲發薪金由於員工打卡混亂所致。 <br />\n<br />\n阿志又透露公司曾要求連續工作36小時，期間僅休息兩小時，「一早一夜，有時會唔適應，會擔心有意外，但要搵食都無辦法啦」，亦試過連續14日工作，期間沒有提供休息日，阿威亦指將會向勞工處尋求協助。 <br />\n有年輕員工遭拖欠逾２萬薪酬 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而19歲的職場新鮮人張先生，今年8月7日入職，而JTC Workshop則自10月起拖欠薪金，涉及28,000元</span>。他指過往公司於每月7日以支票方式出糧，他最後僅於10月中收到9月薪酬，其後一直追問上司及僱主亦不得要領，「覺得世界好恐佈，唔係自己諗得咁簡單」。上司於12月2日後就再無為其安排任何工作，亦未有表明將其解僱。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，被拖欠3個月薪金的朱先生表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">上周四(15日)致電向負責人Terry查詢欠薪情況，對方直認不諱，「係呀，咁點呀？」至今未有提出任何解決方案，張與朱二人早前已向勞工處求助</span>。《香港01》致電負責人Terry，對方僅指事件將於勞工處處理，不作回應。而涉事公司JTC Workshop近日於Facebook貼文，以12,000元起招聘司機。"},{"pid":"de217ac3c2fe62cdb6a1204eb0400dcd400895be","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff629d830aa5ecf5ee00ab154c5e2612bfe90902","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84eceec4154f824f97ee931d65c67cd224ddca1f","tid":255233,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"勞工處啦 post上嚟有咩用？"},{"pid":"cc3acdfaf7464de47413e77b7e74ccae45ffac32","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勞工處啦 post上嚟有咩用？</blockquote><br />\n警惕世人"},{"pid":"fdfcc3feb3db76e6ef7ba9acf8929c8eb65f261b","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1152e397ce976b28637b3af2e55f8f9a1aa1fd8","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53770a2ff3929be3048ebe9cd3fd478e33273b6a","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e381fea71d69c64dafa56fca2023ee00517cf97d","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"633df79a23d1a5d13c8136864154e23805afb028","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d090d8333791d0aa6d501a7c839813c383340bcf","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71cb234d5672d08fdf256f07b868a481628ea7c7","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6a7d1cfcd6a6e6655ff6c8e0bfcb1b264927b26","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ace2dd2b741d58f3e7afbc4bc0170ecff70077e9","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"538958344db4790f3183c7b3e4e9e9a8b30c2de5","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b039ac17e15962cde5f0ddc8153c51eb68dc7f3","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4306fac1f24ad56a8344f2f21411732dcca69107","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2c483f8fc17018e24cb29185faa4a4d4d8af943","tid":255233,"uid":78517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}